          "block_content": "While manyyoung people wereenjoyingthesummevacation,achBonner was workinghishadest.ah started walking from Valrico, Florida, his hometown, on Christmas,2009. He reached Los Angeles nine months later in September,2010.He covered atotal of 2,478 miles andraised $120,000 for kidsin need. Along the way,Zach attended school online.His mother,brother and sister took turns to walkor drive together with him.",
